涉嫌实施袭击的组织[[自由朝鲜|自由朝鲜]]（前身为千里马民防）被《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》认为是“秘密异见者组织”、“意图推翻[[金正恩|金正恩]]政权的影子集团”<ref name="Hudson">{{cite news |last1=Hudson |first1=J. |title=A shadowy group trying to overthrow Kim Jong Un allegedly raided a North Korean embassy in broad daylight |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/a-shadowy-group-trying-to-overthrow-kim-jong-un-raided-a-north-korean-embassy-in-broad-daylight/2019/03/15/ae4208a4-c451-4886-b608-f5ac1f182d3d_story.html?noredirect=on |accessdate=2019-03-31 |work=Washington Post |date=2019-03-15 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190331114147/https://www.washingtonpost.com/gdpr-consent/?destination=/world/national-security/a-shadowy-group-trying-to-overthrow-kim-jong-un-raided-a-north-korean-embassy-in-broad-daylight/2019/03/15/ae4208a4-c451-4886-b608-f5ac1f182d3d_story.html%3Fnoredirect%3Don%26 |archivedate=2019-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而他们认为金正恩政府是“放荡、非法政权”<ref name="NBC News">{{cite news |last1=Dilanian |first1=K. |last2=De Luce |first2=D. |last3=Lederman |first3=J. |title=North Korea calls Madrid embassy raid 'grave terrorist attack,' demands investigation |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/north-korea-calls-investigation-madrid-embassy-raid-n989271 |accessdate=2019-04-01 |work=NBC News |date=2019-03-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190401120801/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/north-korea-calls-investigation-madrid-embassy-raid-n989271 |archivedate=2019-04-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据称，自由朝鲜的成员最初为[[脱北者|脱北者]]，但朝鲜专家约书亚·斯坦顿（{{lang|en|Joshua Stanton}}）认为缺乏证据表明所涉人员中甚至有朝鲜人<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://freekorea.us/2019/03/18/chollima-civil-defense-just-became-a-serious-threat-to-kim-jong-uns-misrule|title=Chollima Civil Defense just became a serious threat to Kim Jong-un's misrule (Update: No, it didn't.)|date=2019-03-18|website=freekorea.us|access-date=2019-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510132346/https://freekorea.us/2019/03/18/chollima-civil-defense-just-became-a-serious-threat-to-kim-jong-uns-misrule/|archive-date=2019-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Lankov">{{cite web |last1=Lankov |first1=A. |title=What to make of a mysterious break-in at the North Korean embassy in Madrid |url=https://www.nknews.org/2019/03/what-to-make-of-a-mysterious-break-in-at-the-north-korean-embassy-in-madrid |website=NK News |accessdate=2019-03-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190327003633/https://www.nknews.org/2019/03/what-to-make-of-a-mysterious-break-in-at-the-north-korean-embassy-in-madrid |archivedate=2019-03-27 |date=2019-03-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。事发两天前，组织的网站招募现场特工、保安和现场情报人员，而这份广告是为曾住在中国且“愿意献身北方解放事业”的年轻人量身定制的<ref name="O'Carroll">{{cite web |last1=O'Carroll |first1=C. |title=Joseon Youth previously recruiting "field agents," with positions open to 16-34 year olds |url=https://www.nknews.org/2019/04/opaque-group-seeking-volunteers-to-help-liberate-north-korea-suspends-website/ |website=NK News |accessdate=2019-04-01 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190401133257/https://www.nknews.org/2019/04/opaque-group-seeking-volunteers-to-help-liberate-north-korea-suspends-website/ |archivedate=2019-04-01 |date=2019-04-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[塔夫茨大学|塔夫茨大学]]的{{le|李成允|Sung-Yoon Lee}}认为，该组织“是首个已知的抵抗朝鲜运动，这使得其活动非常有新闻价值”<ref name="Hudson" />。{{le|朝鲜人权委员会|Committee for Human Rights in North Korea}}执行董事{{le|格雷格·斯卡拉托尤|Greg Scarlatoiu}}表示，“这是我们首次在朝鲜以外地区看到有组织的、明显的军事抵抗”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thenation.com/article/did-the-cia-orchestrate-an-attack-on-the-north-korean-embassy-spain-cia/|title=Did the CIA Orchestrate an Attack on the North Korean Embassy in Spain?|last=Shorrock|first=Tim|date=2019-05-02|access-date=2019-05-10|issn=0027-8378|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509235704/https://www.thenation.com/article/did-the-cia-orchestrate-an-attack-on-the-north-korean-embassy-spain-cia/|archive-date=2019-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

事发前，美国总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]即将与金正恩进行进一步会谈，商讨朝鲜提议的[[无核化|无核化]]计划<ref name="Hudson" />；之前两国于2019年1月在越南[[河内|河内]]举行的峰会上谈判破裂，双方关系进一步恶化<ref name="Hudson" />。

马德里朝鲜大使馆位于宁静<ref name="Lankov" />、富庶的{{le|阿拉瓦卡区|Aravaca}}北部郊区<ref name="González">{{cite news |last1=González |first1=M. |last2=Dolz |first2=P. O. |title=CIA implicated in attack on North Korean embassy in Madrid |url=https://elpais.com/elpais/2019/03/13/inenglish/1552464196_279320.html |accessdate=2019-03-31 |work=El País |date=2019-03-13 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190313181049/https://elpais.com/elpais/2019/03/13/inenglish/1552464196_279320.html |archivedate=2019-03-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>的达里奥·阿帕里西奥街43号<ref name="Dolz">{{cite news |last1=Dolz |first1=P. O. |title=Spain investigates alleged attack on North Korean embassy in Madrid |url=https://elpais.com/elpais/2019/02/27/inenglish/1551264832_928940.html |accessdate=2019-03-31 |work=El País |date=2019-02-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190329033402/https://elpais.com/elpais/2019/02/27/inenglish/1551264832_928940.html |archivedate=2019-03-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang|en|43 Darío Aparicio}}），由两层高的<ref name="BBCb">{{cite news |last1=BBC News |title=North Korea says Madrid embassy raid was 'grave terror attack' |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-47553804 |accessdate=2019-03-31 |work=BBC |date=2019-03-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190331180204/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-47764093 |archivedate=2019-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>“豪华别墅”<ref name="De La Cal">{{cite news |last1=Herraiz |first1=P. |last2=De La Cal |first2=L. |title=La Policía encontró un arsenal en la embajada de Corea del Norte |url=https://www.elmundo.es/espana/2019/03/14/5c895241fc6c83cf468b45a1.html |accessdate=2019-04-01 |work=El Mundo |date=2019-03-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331224512/https://www.elmundo.es/espana/2019/03/14/5c895241fc6c83cf468b45a1.html |archivedate=2019-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及一座游泳池组成<ref name="BBCb"/>，四周棕榈树环绕<ref name="Dolz2019c"/>。大楼位于一片仍未开发的开阔土地的正中央，有助于该地区的自然排水<ref name="De La Cal"/>。《[[国家报|国家报]]》指出，自大使[[金革哲|金革哲]]2017年被驱逐出境以来，只有一名外交官和他的直系亲属在使馆内，过着相对“斯巴达式”的生活<ref name="Dolz2019c">{{cite news |last1=Dolz |first1=P. O. |title='Political espionage' suspected in attack on North Korean embassy in Madrid |url=https://elpais.com/elpais/2019/03/04/inenglish/1551696617_289577.html |accessdate=2019-04-01 |work=El País |date=2019-03-15 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190315215303/https://elpais.com/elpais/2019/03/04/inenglish/1551696617_289577.html |archivedate=2019-03-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，邻居表示使馆在事发前一天曾举行盛大的派对，受到当地人关注<ref name="De La Cal"/>。

==事件==
{{Quotebox|quote=尽管全世界的情报部门热衷于从外国大使馆窃取机密资料或安装窃听设备是公开的秘密，这样张扬、暴力的占领行为还是相对罕见的。<ref name="Lankov" />|source=俄罗斯朝鲜问题专家[[安德烈·兰科夫|安德烈·兰科夫]]|align=left|width=25em|bgcolor=#FFFFF0}}

2019年2月22日，星期五<ref name="Minder">{{cite news |last1=Minder |first1=R. |title=Spain Investigates Possible Attack at North Korean Embassy |accessdate=2019-03-31 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/27/world/europe/spain-north-korea-embassy-attack.html |work=The New York Times |date=2019-02-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190301120719/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/27/world/europe/spain-north-korea-embassy-attack.html |archivedate=2019-03-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，{{le|洪昌|Adrian Hong}}{{Refn|洪是[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]]校友，曾参与美国人权主义[[自由北韓|自由北韓]]的成立工作<ref name="White">{{cite news |last1=Mount |first1=I. |last2=White |first2=E. |last3=Buseong |first3=K. |title=A tale of daring, violence and intrigue from a North Korea embassy |url=https://www.ft.com/content/a8a33f6a-515f-11e9-b401-8d9ef1626294 |accessdate=2019-03-31 |work=Financial Times |date=2019-03-29 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190329090521/https://www.ft.com/content/a8a33f6a-515f-11e9-b401-8d9ef1626294 |archivedate=2019-03-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是[[朝鲜研究院|朝鲜研究院]]（{{lang|en|Joseon Institute}}）的成员<ref name="O'Carroll" />。英国广播公司记者劳拉·比克（{{lang|en|Laura Bicker}}）认为洪昌是“朝鲜知名的社运人士”，曾帮助脱北者逃亡<ref name="BBCc"/>；另据《[[金融时报_(英国)|金融时报]]》报道，他的助手曾表示“他和美国情报部门有联系”<ref name="White"/>。洪昌于2006年因涉嫌帮助当地的脱北者在中国被捕<ref name="White"/>。另一名脱北者姜哲焕认为，虽说洪昌曾供职于“主流”[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]，但最终转而逐渐活跃于“秘密地下活动”<ref name="White"/>，准备即将发生的“大变局”<ref name="Shin">{{cite web |last1=Smith |first1=J. |last2=Shin |first2=H. |title='A target on the back': North Korea embassy raid thrusts shadowy group into the spotlight |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-spain-northkorea-group/a-target-on-the-back-north-korea-embassy-raid-thrusts-shadowy-group-into-the-spotlight-idUSKCN1R817K?il=0 |website=Reuters |accessdate=2019-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401192516/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-spain-northkorea-group/a-target-on-the-back-north-korea-embassy-raid-thrusts-shadowy-group-into-the-spotlight-idUSKCN1R817K?il=0 |archivedate=2019-04-01 |date=2019-03-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年，洪昌声称[[阿拉伯之春|阿拉伯之春]]起义是“为朝鲜举行的盛装彩排”，曾前往利比亚更亲密地研究利比亚<ref name="Shin"/>|group=注}}应邀会见当时使馆内官阶最高的外交官、{{le|专员|Attaché|商务专员}}徐燕石（{{lang|en|Yun Suk So}}）<ref name="Ryall">{{cite news |last1=Ryall |first1=J. |last2=Badcock |first2=J. |title=Was North Korea's vital 'transformation computer' taken in raid on Madrid embassy? |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2019/03/26/raid-north-koreas-madrid-embassy-may-provide-key-codes/ |accessdate=2019-03-31 |work=The Telegraph |date=2019-03-26 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190327174345/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2019/03/26/raid-north-koreas-madrid-embassy-may-provide-key-codes/ |archivedate=2019-03-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而洪昌之前表示徐是他的熟人<ref name="BBCb"/>。两周前，洪昌化名假公司斯通男爵资本（{{lang|en|Baron Stone Capital}}）的管理伙伴赵马修（{{lang|en|Matthew Chao}}）与徐进行简单会谈，商讨公司在朝鲜投资的可能性<ref name="White"/>。

洪昌获准进入大楼后，他的随从紧随其后进入<ref name="BBCb"/>。一种说法是，洪昌是在室内的露台<ref name="White"/>等待专员出现时<ref name="Ryall"/>，自行让随从进入的<ref name="Ryall"/>{{Refn|宣喜告诉警察，她认为他们也可能是爬围墙进入的<ref name="Dolz2019c"/>，而《[[世界报_(西班牙)|世界报]]》确认围墙很容易攀爬<ref name="De La Cal"/>。|group=注}}。这些人是10名蒙面人士<ref name="González" /><ref name="Hudson" />，其中只有一位是30岁以下的模样<ref name="Shin"/>，事发后被指身型为亚洲人，操[[朝鲜语|朝鲜语]]<ref name="Hudson" />。他们可能在使馆外的空地聚集，这比在主路的前门附近游荡相比，吸引的关注要少得多<ref name="De La Cal"/>。一行人[[巴拉克拉瓦头套|巴拉克拉瓦头套]]蒙面，疑似持有仿制枪<ref name="González" />、金属棒、砍刀和匕首<ref name="Ryall"/>，还带着一把{{Convert|3.8|metre|foot}}的伸缩梯子<ref name="White"/>，以及33卷双面胶<ref name="Sevastopulo">{{cite news |last1=Mount |first1=I. |last2=Sevastopulo |first2=D. |title=Spain says leader of North Korea embassy raid contacted FBI |url=https://www.ft.com/content/2e402884-4ff5-11e9-9c76-bf4a0ce37d49 |accessdate=2019-04-01 |work=Financial Times |date=2019-03-26 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190326220339/https://www.ft.com/content/2e402884-4ff5-11e9-9c76-bf4a0ce37d49 |archivedate=2019-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在场有8名<ref name="González" />使馆成员和嘉宾<ref name="Dolz" />，其中一位是朝鲜的建筑系学生<ref name="De La Cal"/>；所有人被绳索<ref name="Hudson" />、手铐和[[束線帶|束線帶]]捆绑<ref name="Ryall"/>，头套<ref name="Hudson" />袋子<ref name="González" />。匪徒审问威胁了使馆的职员<ref name="González" /><ref name="González" />，手法被认为“非常暴力”<ref name="González" />。后来两名职员要求医疗救助<ref name="González" />，主要是因受到多次重击，身体出现瘀伤<ref name="Dolz" />。匪徒的主要目的疑似为使馆的专员，尝试说服他们叛逃，不服从便殴打<ref name="BBCb"/>，还问了他金革哲在使馆期间的事情<ref name="De La Cal"/>。最终他们把他绑在了地下室<ref name="BBCb"/>。
